{"tid":1763391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係旺角搭巴士，塞左好耐","createTime":"2019-11-30T09:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T04:56:22.000Z","uid":53386,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7a3619b16cb8877df9c87f95da046fc6972984","tid":1763391,"uid":53386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"頭先係旺角搭巴士，塞左好耐，因為d交通燈好多都壞左，仔仔問我：爸爸，d差人叔叔去左邊，無人係度指揮交通既？我話：係囉，可能有野做，唔得閒啦。<br />\n<br />\n過左一陣，有人（著住&rdquo;我係香港人&rdquo;既衫）出黎指揮交通，口罩都無帶。<br />\n<br />\n堅感動！多謝你地！<br />\n<br />\n我都想問，d 警察去晒邊？出足糧俾你，旺角咁多人你都唔派人出黎指揮交通！"},{"pid":"00de6327131d2a95ef1fc9853736e67f2bff13e0","tid":1763391,"uid":333741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"太子開始塞 吾知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290a5a1eeba0b12a511ee63f3d9bc280c661eb88","tid":1763391,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FdePAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FdePAe.jpg&h=0121ecc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YqdkGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YqdkGU.jpg&h=92fe9709&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21ya7mV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21ya7mV.jpg&h=591af705&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NFs9Ag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NFs9Ag.jpg&h=28eaa3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqtZgfh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqtZgfh.jpg&h=fb811407&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5RcBfi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5RcBfi.jpg&h=74193287&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJE2d1Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%