replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:56:22.000Z","msg":"想捐錢但除左星火、立場又唔知可以捐去邊？入嚟呢個Channel，Admin會不定期介紹一啲值得課金支持嘅機構、眾籌比大家。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKersFund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKersFund&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=6979dae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKersFund</a><br />\n<br />\n#眾籌<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Democracy Council (HKDC)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/US4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2FUS4HK&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5590a484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/US4HK</a><br />\n<br />\nBackground︰<br />\nHKDC works to preserve Hong Kong&rsquo;s basic freedoms, the rule of law, and autonomy as promised under the &ldquo;one country two systems&rdquo; model and enshrined in the Basic Law and the Sino-British Joint Declaration by:<br />\n<br />\n⚪Informing US policymakers, media and the public on threats and erosions to Hong Kong&rsquo;s democracy and basic freedoms,<br />\n⚪Amplifying influential US voices and support for Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy,<br />\n⚪Providing an independent US platform for Hong Kong&rsquo;s pro-democracy and civil society voices,<br />\n⚪Increasing public support for Hong Kong&rsquo;s distinct political identity and system in the US and around the globe.<br />\n<br />\n目標眾籌金額︰<br />\nUS$250,000 (目前已籌得US$110,000)<br />\n<br />\n100% of your support goes toward:<br />\n⚪A permanent, full-time DC office (20%)<br />\n⚪A professional team of staff and trained members to educate Congress, State Department, and the White House and keep Hong Kong a US priority (40%)<br />\n⚪Training for supporters on how to impact US policies related to Hong Kong (20%)<br />\n⚪Events, press conferences, and testimonies featuring Hong Kongers and experts to amplify all voices defending human rights and democracy in Hong Kong (20%)<br />\n<br />\n香港民主委員會（HKDC）係早前通過嘅《香港人權及民主法案》付出咗相對多嘅努力，例如︰和美國政界接觸、與議員進行游說工作。目前美國政界積極籌備緊另一條制裁法案《Hong Kong Be Water Act》，所以HKDC未來仍然需要資金營運。<br />\n<br />\n相關連結︰<br />\nHKDC Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkdc_us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkdc_us&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=2794860d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkdc_us</a><br />\n蘋果報導: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2P1aSgM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P1aSgM&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5ea04d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2P1aSgM</a><br />\n黃之鋒Twitter有關HKDC嘅Post: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2L8092T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2L8092T&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=966da90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2L8092T</a>"}]}